text: Eloy Songao Inos (September 26, 1949 - December 28, 2015) was an American politician. He was born in the Commonwealth of the Northern Mariana Islands. Inos, a member of the Republican Party, was the Governor of the Northern Mariana Islands. He previously served as Lieutenant Governor. Inos died on December 28, 2015 in Seattle, Washington while recovering from open heart surgery at the age of 66. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Deaths from surgical complications Category:Governors of the Northern Mariana Islands Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:Lieutenant Governors of the Northern Mariana Islands
